NOTE ON DATA LICENSING

This MIT license covers the pipeline SOURCE CODE only. The external datasets the
pipeline downloads and the cached responses redistributed under data/cache/ carry
their own licenses and terms of use, which you must observe:

  * DepMap 24Q4 (Broad Institute)        — CC BY 4.0
  * GBmap core atlas (CELLxGENE Census)  — per contributing-study terms
  * Lake et al. 2018 (GEO GSE97930)      — per GEO / original publication
  * GTEx v8                               — per GTEx data use terms
  * UCSC Xena / TCGA / Toil recompute     — per TCGA and Xena terms
  * Open Targets, ChEMBL, DGIdb, UniProt  — per each resource's license (mostly CC BY / CC0)

Cite the original data sources when using their data. See docs/METHODS.md for
versions and accessions.
